    <p>Don't get me wrong I'm all for alternatives to the current system.</p>
<p>However, two things really bother me about Bitcoin and other eCurrencies;</p>
<p>1.&nbsp; Exchangability is&nbsp;dependent on the internet.&nbsp; No internet and Bitcoin or any other eCurrency is worthless.</p>
<p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Total dependence on the availability of electricity.&nbsp; No electricity no power and again eCurrencies are effectively worthless.</p>
<p>If the shit REALLY hits the fan you're better off with bic lighters, whisky, chocolate, ammo etc.&nbsp; I recommend reading the experiences of&nbsp;residents of Sarajevo during the Bosnian civil war.&nbsp;</p>
